# Local file mode: set this to a CSV or plain-text file path when running without Supabase.
# The file must be reachable by the browser (e.g. place it in the public/ folder).
# CSV format: name,organization,email (header row optional). Plain text: one name per line.
# In npm run dev, local manual entry auto-saves back to this CSV path.
# Example: VITE_LOCAL_NAMES_FILE=/names.csv
VITE_LOCAL_NAMES_FILE=/names.csv
